cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.AR 

This paper is focused on the implementation and evaluation of coverage enhancement features of NB-IoT, which is a wireless communication technology for the Internet of Things (IoT). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization algorithms and resource allocation, which are related to cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper discusses the reliability and security of the network, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
